{"tid":2008372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Steam支那】加設「防沉迷代碼」 。支那玩家崩潰！","createTime":"2020-05-09T04:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T02:07:43.000Z","uid":202464,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3e4f36689ff110dd54a500187e9240d7296d30ed","tid":2008372,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:00:34.000Z","msg":"近期對岸網友從Steam 5月5日的更新文件中挖出了全新的代碼條目，在簡體中文語言文本中，居然多增加了一行名為「SteamChina_Overlay_DurationControl_ExitSoon_Night」的控制項，簡單來說，該控制項的註解翻成中文大概是這樣：<br />\n<br />\n「您受到＂防沉迷系統＂限制，且已達到今日遊戲時間限制。您必須現在退出遊戲，休息一下，明天再來。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，Steam的啟動捷徑後面加上「-dev -steamchina 」參數，就會進入遊戲中跳出5秒的全螢幕防沉迷宣導。<br />\n<br />\n其他玩家也發現其他防沉迷代碼，像是玩超過2小時就會跳出新通知、超過3小時就會開始扣經驗，而玩到5小時則會直接關閉遊戲，需要等到明天早上8點才能重新進入遊戲等等的英文註解。<br />\n<br />\n而其中誇張的是，在英文語言版本的文版中，並沒有這項控制項的存在，這也讓分析數據的對岸網友覺得很傻眼"},{"pid":"c7b18a38de6f45f552c2ef085a46738ecf8277ca","tid":2008372,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b668ea4ebb14f56bba6acf42d9f470f175b6e15d","tid":2008372,"uid":20518,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"唔係跳出黎考你毛語錄/習語錄應該感恩"},{"pid":"04f4273e468e43541c57313999d1c0b8e53711bc","tid":2008372,"uid":202340,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:08:07.000Z","msg":"轉頭香港都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce7bcc5bbfa4c68d9636e1a4230fbf2b8cc64e7","tid":2008372,"uid":202464,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"04f4273e468e43541c57313999d1c0b8e53711bc","tid":2008372,"uid":202340,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:08:07.000Z","msg":"轉頭香港都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/